# OpenClaw Project Overview

OpenClaw is a multi-channel AI gateway and personal assistant supporting WhatsApp, Telegram, Slack, Discord, Signal, iMessage, and more.

## Tech Stack

- **Core**: TypeScript (ESM), Node.js ≥22.12.0, pnpm 10.x monorepo
- **Build**: tsdown (bundling), tsgo (type-checking)
- **Lint/Format**: oxlint + oxfmt (NOT ESLint/Prettier)
- **Test**: Vitest with V8 coverage
- **Native apps**: Swift (macOS/iOS), Kotlin (Android)
- **Skills**: Python (Ruff + pytest)
- **UI**: Lit web components (legacy decorators)

## Key Directories

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/` | Core source (CLI, commands, channels, agents, config) |
| `extensions/` | Channel plugins (telegram, discord, slack, matrix, etc.) |
| `packages/` | Internal packages |
| `ui/` | Web Control UI (Lit) |
| `apps/` | Native apps (macos, ios, android) |
| `docs/` | Mintlify-hosted documentation |
| `skills/` | Python skill scripts |
| `scripts/` | Build, test, CI scripts |

## Essential Commands

```
pnpm install        # Install dependencies
pnpm build          # Build dist (tsdown + tsgo)
pnpm check          # Format + typecheck + lint
pnpm test           # Unit tests (Vitest)
pnpm test:e2e       # E2E tests
pnpm gateway:watch  # Dev mode with hot reload
pnpm format:fix     # Auto-fix formatting (oxfmt)
```

## Personal Fork Notes

This is a private fork. When contributing upstream, keep PRs focused (one topic per PR). Code comments in English to stay consistent with upstream.

Interested areas: local LLM integration, ComfyUI extension development.
